items.title: Trump clashes with Australian journalist over business deals in office
items.description: The US leader said the journalist was "hurting Australia very much" as he said he would meet the country's PM "very soon".

items.title: Newborn baby buried alive in India fights for her life
items.description: The 20-day-old girl was found by chance when a shepherd heard faint cries from under a mound of earth.

items.title: Togo leader's sister-in-law arrested after calling for end to family rule
items.description: Marguerite Gnakadé has become a vocal critic of Togo's long-serving leader Faure Gnassingbé.

items.title: Jimmy Kimmel taken off air over Charlie Kirk comments
items.description: The late-night host said on Monday that Trump's allies were "doing everything they can to score political points from" Kirk's death.

items.title: Australia announces higher emissions cuts by 2035
items.description: The country is one of the world's biggest carbon emitters per capita.
